<author>nạjy fw̉ạd, bhyr ạ̹dwạrd</author>
<title>mn ly swạk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (mn ly swạk yḥmyny .. mn kl sẖriⁿ qạdmiⁿ)2
 mn ly swạk yrwyny .. mn kl nbʿiⁿ fạỷḍiⁿ
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̉nt ạ̹lhy lạ swạk)4
 2- (mn ly swạk sydy .. ymlạ̉ frạgẖ wḥdty)2
 mn ly swạk mrsẖdy .. yhms ly fy kẖlwty
 3- (kyf ạ̉kẖạf fy ạlṭryq .. wạ̉nt ly nbʿ ạlrjạʾ)2
 kyf bdwnk ạ̉syr .. fy ʿạlmiⁿ blạ ʿzạʾ
 4- (ậty ạ̹lyk ḍạrʿaⁿạ .. fạnẓr ạ̹lyã mn ʿlạk)2
 ạunẓr ạ̹lyã sạndaⁿạ .. ḥty̱ ạ̉ʿysẖ fy rḍạk</lyrics>
</song>